Three use cases for gitHub classroom
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3j1BaUw53pM
In this panel three professors shared how they used GitHub for their courses: 
* Omar Shaikh (SFSU) GitHub + Travis CI for automated grading (https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qimc_OGD75E)
* S. Monisha Pulimood (TCNJ) Collaborating on real-world projects 
* David Malan (Harvard) Custom tools for CS50
